{"title":"护理","uid":"3727cb78a6cab04b75076473baee6eb4","slug":"nurse","date":"2022-04-07T05:25:31.000Z","updated":"2022-04-07T09:38:08.487Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/nurse.json","keywords":"笔记","cover":[],"content":"<h1 id=\"痘痘\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#痘痘\"></a> 痘痘</h1>\n<h2 id=\"痘痘等级医学上-一般\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#痘痘等级医学上-一般\"></a> 痘痘等级（医学上 一般）</h2>\n<h3 id=\"一级轻度\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#一级轻度\"></a> 一级轻度</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>粉刺（不泛红）</li>\n<li>治疗建议（一般）\n<ul>\n<li>长痘痘外部进行治疗</li>\n<li><img src=\"../images/nurse/image-20220407133204902.png\" alt=\"image-20220407133204902\"></li>\n<li>可能会有轻微的刺激，过一段时间，会消失的，属于正常现象。</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"二级轻至中度\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#二级轻至中度\"></a> 二级（轻至中度）</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>炎性丘疹（发红，无明显脓液）</li>\n<li>青春痘的最大组成部分</li>\n<li>大多数是由于清理不当或者性激素分泌旺盛而产生的。常伴随一些细菌，这些细菌会使毛囊鸡毛囊周围发生非特殊炎症反应。即肉眼所能看到的发红。</li>\n<li><img src=\"../images/nurse/image-20220407134037627.png\" alt=\"image-20220407134037627\"></li>\n<li>白天涂抹过氧化苯甲酰：对痘痘部位进行消炎杀菌；夜间使用维A酸来释放毛囊中的堵塞物</li>\n<li>涂抹过氧化苯甲酰：可能会感到皮肤刺激，也可能会面临干燥和脱皮（所以要注意防晒补水和保湿）</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"三级中度\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#三级中度\"></a> 三级中度</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>除有粉刺和炎性丘疹外，主要表现为脓疱（内有脓液，发红，可被挤出）</li>\n<li>脓液：一般由坏死的白细胞和机体防卫组织液够成</li>\n<li>除了涂抹过氧化苯甲酰和维A酸外，还应口服四环素，米诺环素，或者红霉素等药物。抑制毛囊口的细菌繁殖来达到治本的目的。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"四级重度\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#四级重度\"></a> 四级重度</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>除以上情况外，还有结节，囊肿或瘢痕（质地发硬，内有脓液，难以挤出）</li>\n<li>除了用到以上药物外，可能还需要用到光动力治疗。（价格超贵）</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"../images/nurse/image-20220407135915003.png\" alt=\"image-20220407135915003\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"../images/nurse/image-20220407135934291.png\" alt=\"image-20220407135934291\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"../images/nurse/image-20220407140004654.png\" alt=\"image-20220407140004654\"></p>\n","text":" 痘痘 痘痘等级（医学上 一般） 一级轻度 粉刺（不泛红） 治疗建议（一般） 长痘痘外部进行治疗 可能会有轻微的刺激，过一段时间，会消失的，属于正常现象。 二级（轻至中度） 炎性丘疹（发红，无明显脓液） 青春痘的最大组成部分 大多数是由于清理不当或者性激素分泌旺盛而产生的。常伴随...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":475,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%97%98%E7%97%98\"><span class=\"toc-text\"> 痘痘</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%97%98%E7%97%98%E7%AD%89%E7%BA%A7%E5%8C%BB%E5%AD%A6%E4%B8%8A-%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC\"><span class=\"toc-text\"> 痘痘等级（医学上 一般）</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%80%E7%BA%A7%E8%BD%BB%E5%BA%A6\"><span class=\"toc-text\"> 一级轻度</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BA%8C%E7%BA%A7%E8%BD%BB%E8%87%B3%E4%B8%AD%E5%BA%A6\"><span class=\"toc-text\"> 二级（轻至中度）</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%89%E7%BA%A7%E4%B8%AD%E5%BA%A6\"><span class=\"toc-text\"> 三级中度</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%9B%9B%E7%BA%A7%E9%87%8D%E5%BA%A6\"><span class=\"toc-text\"> 四级重度</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Aurora","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"智能家居（物联网）","uid":"c7b0c53a51da6bfa1ffd1a25fdad8f30","slug":"stm32-esp8288-ai","date":"2022-04-07T14:21:50.000Z","updated":"2022-04-09T01:48:36.877Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/stm32-esp8288-ai.json","keywords":"笔记","cover":[],"text":" 【小程序】基于mpvue框架开发微信小程序基础环境配置 【小程序】小程序效果展示分析 ","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":48,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[],"author":{"name":"Aurora","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"","